Name: Plunderer Captain's Seal
AttributesDescription:
Recovers 3% of the Resonator's HP per second and deals 600% Electro DMG to nearby targets upon the sixth HP recovery.

This Token can be used up to 2 times in Whimpering Wastes.
BgDescription: A pirate ship wandering in the mist, known for instilling everlasting fear with the simplest tricks.
